Keep
scammers
busy

We harness the power of artificial intelligence to combat online scammers.

Our mission is to waste scammers time by responding to their emails in the most time-consuming way possible. The more time spent talking to our bot, the less time scammers have to target real people.

Join us in the fight against online scams and help make the internet a safer place.

Re:Scam generates an endless array of convincing and strategic personas, to keep scammers within never-ending conversations. By keeping scammers busy, the bot continuously optimises itself, discarding less effective personas and crafting new ones.

The project

Kiwis lost over 200 million NZD to scammers in 2023. So Re:Scam has returned, new and improved, to fight online scammers once again. Netsafe is relaunching this bot, to ensure that New Zealanders have an AI weapon at their disposal to keep them safe online and keep scammers busy.
